  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      IVIg exert a variety of different immunomodulatory effects and several mechanism of action
      have been proposed for IVIg. In this study the role of IVIg on short term nerve conduction in
      patients with immune-mediated neuropathies will be explored.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
